description: With our impression-based model, the 20-60% commission is a thing of the past. You pay us $12, we put you in front of 1,000 qualified buyers. Simple as that. Thanks to our unique user-experiences on mobile, web, and social, our sell-through rate (sales per 1,000 impressions) out-performs the biggest names in online advertising by more than 5x.
name: Benjacoin
